---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for Amply — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <div class="page-container">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1 class="display-lg">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you place a rental order through Amply, we collect the information you provide directly: your name, phone number, email address, city, and event details. We do not collect payment information — payment is handled separately via UPI or bank transfer after order confirmation.</p>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use your information solely to fulfil your rental order — confirming availability, coordinating delivery and setup, and communicating about your booking. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2>3. Order Data</h2>
      <p>Order details submitted through our checkout form are captured via Netlify Forms and stored securely. We retain order records for accounting and service fulfilment purposes. You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us.</p>

      <h2>4. Cookies & Analytics</h2>
      <p>Our website may use minimal analytics to understand how visitors use the site (e.g. page views). We do not use advertising cookies or track you across other websites. No personally identifiable information is collected through analytics.</p>

      <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable precautions to protect your information. Our website is served over HTTPS. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

      <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>Our site is hosted on Netlify. Order forms are processed via Netlify Forms. These services have their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review them.</p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your personal information. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@amply.in">hello@amply.in</a>.</p>

      <h2>8. Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, reach us at:<br />
      <strong>Amply</strong><br />
      Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India<br />
      <a href="mailto:hello@amply.in">hello@amply.in</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-container { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 24px 96px; }
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-hairline); padding-bottom: 32px; }
  .page-header h1 { margin: 0 0 8px; }
  .last-updated { font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-mute); margin: 0; }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { .page-container { padding: 40px 20px 72px; } }
</style>
